page.title: 15Breeding Dogs in Calne.
page.content: German Shepherd dogs first came from Germany.They were used for herding sheep.My father is breeding them.My bitch Bella has had five pups.Before I go to school, we give them Weetbix or porridge.In the evening we give them minced meat and milk. We have Labrador pups as well.We feed them the same food but less,yet they are really fat. We mated our yellow Labrador bitch Tessa with a black Labrador.Two of our pups went to Dodington Estate,to be trained as gun dogs. Our German Shepherd pups,also called Alastains we sell for 130 pounds.Our Labrador pups go for 80 pounds. My name is Keeley Agar and I live in Oxford Road,Calne.
